<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--
  kerby — bundled AUDIT REPORT template. Renders a conformance-audit Markdown
  report as a single self-contained, shareable HTML file.
  Governed by references/audit.md § 8, which defines the body-markup contract
  (banner + findings tables emitted as raw HTML; everything else Markdown).

  Placeholders: {{TITLE}} {{CONTENT}} {{SOURCE}} {{DATE}}.

  Styling override surface — the :root below:
    BASE tokens (--bg --ink --ink-muted --accent --border --code-bg --font-*
      --radius --measure): overwrite from DESIGN.md when present; else ship as-is.
    STATUS tokens (--sev-*, --notrun-*): semantic (danger/warning/neutral), NOT
      brand — keep fixed so a brand palette can't make "blocker" stop reading as
      danger, or a not-run pass read as clean.
      Override only if DESIGN.md explicitly defines danger/warning tokens.
-->
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<!-- Defense-in-depth behind audit.md § 8 escaping: no script, no external loads,
     no images. The report is self-contained and JS-free — keep it that way so a
     missed escape on untrusted repo content can't beacon or execute. -->
<meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'none'; style-src 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'none'; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'">
<title>{{TITLE}}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:        #fbfaf8;
    --ink:       #1f2937;
    --ink-muted: #6b7280;
    --accent:    #c2410c;
    --border:    #e5e0d8;
    --code-bg:   #f3f1ec;
    --font-body: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    --font-mono: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    --measure:   52rem;
    --radius:    6px;
    --sev-blocker-bg: #f6ddd4; --sev-blocker-ink: #8a2c12;
    --sev-major-bg:   #fbecd2; --sev-major-ink:   #92400e;
    --sev-minor-bg:   #ece9e3; --sev-minor-ink:   #57534e;
    --notrun-bg:      #fdf6e3; --notrun-ink:      #92400e;  /* not-run: amber, must NOT read as a clean pass */
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
  body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .doc { max-width: var(--measure); margin: 0 auto; padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 3rem; }

  h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent); }
  h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 2.2em 0 0.5em; }
  h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 1.8em 0 0.5em; color: var(--ink-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  p { margin: 0 0 1em; }
  a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
  code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.86em; background: var(--code-bg); padding: 0.1em 0.35em; border-radius: 3px; }

  .banner { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); background: #fff; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem; font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.55; margin: 0 0 1.4rem; }
  .banner strong { font-weight: 700; }
  .banner .muted { color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .banner code { background: var(--code-bg); }

  table.findings { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0 0 1.2em; }
  table.findings thead th { text-align: left; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.74rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--ink-muted); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); padding: 0.5em 0.7em; }
  table.findings tbody td { vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.7em 0.7em; }
  table.findings tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  table.findings td:first-child { width: 5.4rem; }
  table.findings td:last-child  { width: 5rem; }
  table.findings td code { background: var(--code-bg); color: var(--ink-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; word-break: break-all; }
  .src { display: block; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-top: 0.15em; }
  .fix { display: block; margin-top: 0.3em; }
  .fix b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

  .sev { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.74rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.18em 0.5em; border-radius: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .sev-blocker { background: var(--sev-blocker-bg); color: var(--sev-blocker-ink); }
  .sev-major   { background: var(--sev-major-bg);   color: var(--sev-major-ink); }
  .sev-minor   { background: var(--sev-minor-bg);   color: var(--sev-minor-ink); }

  .conf { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .conf-observed { color: var(--ink); }
  .conf-inferred { color: var(--ink-muted); font-style: italic; }

  .none { color: var(--ink-muted); font-style: italic; padding: 0.4em 0; }
  .notrun { display: block; background: var(--notrun-bg); color: var(--notrun-ink); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 0.5em 0.75em; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.4em 0; }
  .doc-footer { margin-top: 2.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1.2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .doc-footer ul { margin: 0.3em 0 1em; padding-left: 1.3em; }
  .doc-footer li { margin: 0.2em 0; }
  .doc-footer .canon { font-size: 0.82rem; margin-top: 1.2rem; }

  @media print {
    body { background: #fff; }
    thead { display: table-header-group; }
    tr, table.findings, .banner { break-inside: avoid; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="doc">
{{CONTENT}}
<div class="doc-footer">
  <p class="canon">Markdown is canonical · this HTML is a snapshot of <code>{{SOURCE}}</code> · exported {{DATE}}.</p>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
